<section class='s-marginTop5 s-borderTop2_5 s-marginBottom5 blog-posts-show__featured-investments-section' id='featured-investments-section'>
<div class="blog-posts-show-featured_investments" data-rc="blog/posts/show/featured_investments"><header class='s-marginBottom2 u-textCenter blog-posts-show-featured_investments__header'>
<h2 class='c-condensedTitle s-fontSize30 u-colorBlack s-marginBottom1_5 blog-posts-show-featured_investments__title'>
Chirag’s Sparkle was funded by
807 investors
</h2>
<div class='s-grid'>
<div class='s-grid-colSm8'>
<a class="c-button c-button--large c-button--block blog-posts-show-featured_investments__offering-link" data-type="offering" data-slug="sparkle" href="/sparkle"><div class="c-avatar c-avatar--extra_small blog-posts-show-featured_investments__offering-avatar c-avatar--border c-avatar--sparkle"><img alt="Logo of Sparkle" title="Sparkle" srcset="https://uploads.republic.com/p/offerings/logos/small_2x/000/000/403/403-1580926466-c1b4625a5af1856cb349ff234a6643497d73001f.png 2x" src="https://uploads.republic.com/p/offerings/logos/small/000/000/403/403-1580926466-5a24abc9e25b895216ef26ad1eb8e3057137413e.png" /></div>
View Sparkle
</a></div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="u-displayFlex s-paddingVert1 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investments" data-rc="investment_reasons/shared/featured_investments"><div class='u-flex1 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investments__reason-wrapper'>
<div class="s-fontSize18 u-fontWeight400 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investment" data-rc="investment_reasons/shared/featured_investment"><p class='s-marginBottom1_5 u-colorGray6'>
I love the combination of social cause with a real product that is already in demand. What made my decision easier was the goal of moving into the diaper market. Combined it has a huge potential market. 
</p>
<div class='u-displayFlex u-alignItemsCenter'>
<div class="c-avatar c-avatar--small  js-user_avatar"><img alt="Profile picture of Patrick Craven" title="Patrick Craven" srcset="https://uploads.republic.com/p/users/avatars/small_2x/000/402/264/402264-1570975615-397d72d282330110ed9976b5caf139aa5367753c.jpg 2x" src="https://uploads.republic.com/p/users/avatars/small/000/402/264/402264-1570975615-44129f4be7278892c59a2d0ff2d63b989d84f237.jpg" /></div>
<div class='s-marginLeft1'>
<div class='c-condensedTitle s-fontSize18'>
<span class="js-tooltip_ajax c-link c-link--unstyled u-colorBlack " data-type="user" data-slug="patrick-craven">Patrick Craven</span>
</div>
<div class="c-tag js-tooltip_simple c-tag--active_investor c-tag--extra_small c-tag--thick badges-shared-list_item" data-tippy-content="<div class='s-padding0_5'>
Patrick is a repeat investor on Republic
</div>
" data-tippy-interactive="true" data-rc="badges/shared/list_item">Active investor
</div>
<div class='u-colorGray6 s-fontSize12 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investment__date'>
almost 3 years ago
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='s-borderLeft2_5 s-marginLeft2_5 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investments__vertical-divider'></div>
<div class='u-flex1 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investments__reason-wrapper'>
<div class="s-fontSize18 u-fontWeight400 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investment" data-rc="investment_reasons/shared/featured_investment"><p class='s-marginBottom1_5 u-colorGray6'>
Sparkle is (to my knowledge) the only company with proprietary technology and patents to resolve this huge problem. And they do this in a sustainable, win-win way. Win for the users, the environment, the farmers and the Investors.
</p>
<div class='u-displayFlex u-alignItemsCenter'>
<div class="c-avatar c-avatar--small  js-user_avatar"><img alt="Profile picture of Martin Brenner" title="Martin Brenner" srcset="https://uploads.republic.com/p/users/avatars/small_2x/000/532/472/532472-1578605622-2099af10b3252abc9cf20ac77c51178f8da8d2a8.jpeg 2x" src="https://uploads.republic.com/p/users/avatars/small/000/532/472/532472-1578605622-20b14774fc0b5165e2e4f46347f1c2faa47ebb95.jpeg" /></div>
<div class='s-marginLeft1'>
<div class='c-condensedTitle s-fontSize18'>
<span class="js-tooltip_ajax c-link c-link--unstyled u-colorBlack " data-type="user" data-slug="martin-brenner">Martin Brenner</span>
</div>
<div class="c-tag js-tooltip_simple c-tag--value_add_investor c-tag--extra_small c-tag--thick badges-shared-list_item" data-tippy-content="<div class='s-padding0_5'>
Value-add investors proactively help startups they invest in
</div>
" data-tippy-interactive="true" data-rc="badges/shared/list_item">Value-add investor
</div>
<div class='u-colorGray6 s-fontSize12 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investment__date'>
almost 3 years ago
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='s-borderLeft2_5 s-marginLeft2_5 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investments__vertical-divider'></div>
<div class='u-flex1 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investments__reason-wrapper'>
<div class="s-fontSize18 u-fontWeight400 investment_reasons-shared-featured_investment" data-rc="investment_reasons/shared/featured_investment"><p class='s-marginBottom1_5 u-colorGray6'>
The impact of this product is many fold -- it improves sustainability through a biodegradable product and upcycling of agro waste, it improves the earn abilities of farmers in these communities, and it provides a healthier product for the consumer.
</p>
<div class='u-displayFlex u-alignItemsCenter'>
<div class="c-avatar c-avatar--small  js-user_avatar"><img alt="Profile picture of Amy Slawson" title="Amy Slawson" srcset="https://uploads.republic.com/p/users/avatars/small_2x/000/609/454/609454-1587928346-d04b4d9a6c6ba7ebaa27a32dc86e85b925d0dae5.jpeg 2x" src="https://uploads.republic.com/p/users/avatars/small/000/609/454/609454-1587928346-546a86de139d6de9481c523e7a8900d29a584734.jpeg" /></div>
<div class='s-marginLeft1'>
<div class='c-condensedTitle s-fontSize18'>
<span class="js-tooltip_ajax c-link c-link--unstyled u-colorBlack " data-type="user" data-slug="amy-slawson">Amy Slawson</span>
</div>
<div class="c-tag js-tooltip_simple c-tag--value_add_investor c-tag--extra_small c-tag--thick badges-shared-list_item" data-tippy-content="<div class='s-padding0_5'>
